Package edu.ncsu.csc216.product_backlog.model.backlog

Class BacklogManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.product_backlog.model.backlog.BacklogManager
  • public class BacklogManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that handles the managing of ProductBacklog. In this class this is where the user will do most of the interacting. Users can add, edit, and delete products as well as tasks. They can also completely clear the list of products or reset the manager if there are issues. Users can also load files with products and task and also save their backlog to a file.
    Author:
    Daniel Avisse
